<item>
            <title>[DATAREST-195] Limiting page size</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAREST-195</link>
                <project id="10901" key="DATAREST">Spring Data REST</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently SDR allows to set the page &quot;size&quot; parameter without limiting it. From an unscrupulous user making requests with large &quot;size&quot; parameter could bring down the app. It would be nice to limit &quot;size&quot; parameter at global level as well as individual resource level.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="52010">DATAREST-195</key>
            <summary>Limiting page size</summary>
